# Build output of `dotnet publish` (the same content is already packaged in
# Calcpad-Symbolic-portable-win-x64.exe / the installers). Adding every
# individual DLL/PDB would bloat the repo with thousands of redundant files.
/publish/
# Large binaries (installers, portable zips) are tracked via Git LFS —
# see .gitattributes. NOT excluded anymore.
